aa(lp115
VI think there is no doubt that the sector
p116
aVneeds a complete overhaul,
p117
aVnot just a trimming at the margins.
p118
aVI think it's time for a bold move.
p119
aVI think it's time to upgrade the system.
p120
aVAnd this is why we at the Bertelsmann Foundation
p121
aVhave invested a lot of time and effort
p122
aVthinking about an alternative for the sector.
p123
aVAnd we have developed the first model
p124
aVfor a nonprofit rating agency for sovereign risk,
p125
aVand we call it by its acronym, INCRA.
