aa(lp127
VINCRA would make a difference
p128
aVto the current system
p129
aVby adding another nonprofit player to the mix.
p130
aVIt would be based on a nonprofit model
p131
aVthat would be based on a sustainable endowment.
p132
aVThe endowment would create income
p133
aVthat would allow us to run the operation,
p134
aVto run the rating agency,
p135
aVand it would also allow us
p136
aVto make our ratings publicly available.
p137
aVBut this is not enough to make a difference, right?
p138
aVINCRA would also be based on
p139
aVa very, very clear governance structure
p140
aVthat would avoid any conflict of interest,
p141
aVand it would include many stakeholders from society.
p142
aVINCRA would not only be a European
p143
aVor an American rating agency,
p144
aVit would be a truly international one,
p145
aVin which, in particular, the emerging economies
p146
aVwould have an equal interest,  voice and representation.
